=<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333;">
  Dear Job Seeker,<br><br>
  This daily digest summarizes the results of your automated job search. The Top 5 job matches found in today's run are detailed below, with comprehensive analysis available in your tracking sheet.
</p>

<div style="margin-top: 20px;">
  <h3 style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #0077b5; border-bottom: 2px solid #eeeeee; padding-bottom: 5px;">
    🏆 Top 5 Job Matches
  </h3>

  {{ $json.data.map((item, index) => {
    // Safely replace newlines in Improvements
    const improvements = item.Improvements ? item.Improvements.replace(/
/g, '<br>').replace(/"/g, '&quot;') : 'N/A';
    
    // Choose alternating background color
    const bgColor = index % 2 === 0 ? '#f4f4f4' : '#ffffff';
    
    // Determine score color for visual emphasis
    const score = parseInt(item.Score) || 0;
    const scoreColor = score >= 80 ? 'green' : (score >= 60 ? 'orange' : 'red');

    // Extract the first improvement point
    const topImprovement = improvements.split('<br>')[0] || 'No specific top improvement listed.';

    return `
      <div style="border: 1px solid #dddddd; padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 8px; background-color: ${bgColor};">
        <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #333333;">
          ${index + 1}. ${item.Title} @ ${item.Company}
        </h4>
        <p style="margin: 5px 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">
          <strong>Match Score:</strong> <strong style="color: ${scoreColor}; font-weight: bold;">${item.Score}/100</strong>
          | <strong>Location:</strong> ${item.Location}
          | <strong>Salary:</strong> ${item['Salary '] || 'N/A'}
        </p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
          <a href="${item.Link}" style="color: #0077b5; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">[View Job & Apply]</a>
        </p>
        
        <div style="margin-top: 15px; padding: 10px; border-top: 1px dashed #cccccc;">
          <h5 style="color: #555555; margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 14px;">Top Resume Improvement Action:</h5>
          <span style="font-size: 13px; color: #555; white-space: pre-wrap;">${topImprovement}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    `;
  }).join('') }}
</div>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333; margin-top: 30px;">
  Access the full, filterable list and detailed notes for all jobs (including full cover letters, red flags, and more) here:<br>
  <a href="[YOUR_GOOGLE_SHEET_LINK]" style="color: #0077b5; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 8px;">
    🚀 Open Job Search Tracking Sheet
  </a>
</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px;">
  Best of luck with your job search!
</p>

